          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>The Anti-Deficiency Reform and Enforcement Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill strengthens penalties for federal employees who violate the Anti-Deficiency Act. Additionally, the bill authorizes an agency to award a cash payment to an employee who discloses a potential violation of the Anti-Deficiency Act, and it requires the Inspector General of each agency to assess biennially whether any such violation occurred at the agency.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-02-13T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
